description: Ever Harvest International Group Inc., through its subsidiaries, engages in the development and sale of STEAM education products and services to the primary and secondary school markets in Hong Kong. It develops robotic kits for students at different levels to learn how to build a robot themselves; and provides educators with accessible guides, soft contents, resources, online platform, and physical STEAM education centers. The company was formerly known as Totally Green, Inc. and changed its name to Ever Harvest International Group Inc. in October 2021. Ever Harvest International Group Inc. was incorporated in 2002 and is based in Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong.
